metadata.name: yadzi - Catch Me (Official Video) 1/1
metadata.description:
yadzi - Catch Me (Official Video)

Catch Me is the second single from yadzi's debut EP, 'Into Our Hands'. This is yadzi's first full-length music video.

/ / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / / /

!! Perks !!
If this NFT is collected before the EP is released (early 2023), the collector(s) will have the opportunity to be included in the 'Into Our Hands' cover art & intro track projects (go here for full details & project description: https://mirror.xyz/yadzi.eth/5EZKCjO8n_SDWuJMtNPwWIOrY0qIBU2SneppcxdAdFA).
